%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Basic Text - Show a Message" in
%	Chapter 1 - "Introducing PostScript".
%
%	Caveats:	Requires PostScript Level 2.

/Palatino-Roman 162 selectfont	%  find required font and size
108 36 moveto			%  set current point
52 rotate			%  rotate coordinate system
(PostScript!) show		%  image title on page
showpage			%  display page
